snippet.textDisplay:
Love the argument they are going through. Star shah describes a character that has seen posion in the hearts of the people. 

While zeeshan Ali describes a character that believes love is the only cure. Either he is very immature in his love or has ascended to a level where he understands the pupose of love.

Both of these characters argue till the end but no one wins the argument because both are right. 

The song ask a very basic question whether you believe in love or not?

And i think you gotta love some people and ignore the people that damage your soul.
